  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    COVID-19: epidemiological definitions of outbreaks and clusters
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Description of the criteria used to define the beginning and end of an outbreak or a cluster in particular settings.</p>

  </div>
</div>

